title: UFC 268 Embedded: Vlog Series - Episode 1
author: UFC - Ultimate Fighting Championship
description:
Michael Chandler plans to steal the show at UFC 268. Champ Kamaru Usman pushes his coach; teammate Justin Gaethje gets recognized on a run. Champ Rose Namajunas gets pumped by watching UFC 267.
